{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-154","title":"冷漠轻蔑","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":776,"pageEnd":780,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":16,"duplicateEntryCount":24,"pages":[{"number":776,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"154 冷漠轻蔑"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"coolth [kuːlθ]","headword":"coolth"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.冷静；漠然"},{"type":"entry","text":"unconcern [ˌʌnkənˈsɜːn]","headword":"unconcern"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.不感兴趣；冷淡"},{"type":"entry","text":"inhospitality [ˌɪnhɒspɪˈtæləti]","headword":"inhospitality"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.冷淡；不好客"}]},{"number":777,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"unbending [ˌʌnˈbendɪŋ]","headword":"unbending"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.冷漠的"},{"type":"entry","text":"disdainful [dɪsˈdeɪnfl]","headword":"disdainful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.轻蔑的；鄙视的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎a disdainful look白眼"},{"type":"entry","text":"scornful [ˈskɔːnfl]","headword":"scornful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.轻蔑的；鄙视的"}]},{"number":778,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"sneering [ˈsnɪərɪŋ]","headword":"sneering"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.嘲笑的；轻蔑的"},{"type":"entry","text":"contemptuous term蔑称","headword":"contemptuous term"},{"type":"entry","text":"apathetically [ˌæpəˈθetɪkli]","headword":"apathetically"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 冷淡地；无动于衷地"},{"type":"entry","text":"neglect [nɪˈɡlekt]","headword":"neglect"},{"type":"definition","text":"v./n.忽视；忽略"},{"type":"note","text":"◎emotional neglect情感忽视"}]},{"number":779,"blocks":[]},{"number":780,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"none of my business 不关我的事","headword":"none of my business"},{"type":"entry","text":"have nothing to do with me 与我无关","headword":"have nothing to do with me"},{"type":"entry","text":"laugh at 嘲笑，取笑","headword":"laugh at"},{"type":"entry","text":"look down 轻视","headword":"look down"},{"type":"entry","text":"make fun of 取笑","headword":"make fun of"},{"type":"entry","text":"look down upon 看不起","headword":"look down upon"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：He expressed great contempt for this action.（他对这一行为表示"},{"type":"text","text":"了极度蔑视。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：If I was there, I would act like that, too. （要是我在场，我也会"},{"type":"text","text":"这样做。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I didn't know it would be disdainful.（我当时不知道这很轻"},{"type":"text","text":"蔑。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：You should have thought about it.（你应该考虑到的。）"}]}]}